msgid ""
"If the program is released under the GNU Affero GPL, then add &ldquo;"
"Affero&rdquo; before &ldquo;General&rdquo;, change &ldquo;GPL&rdquo; to "
"&ldquo;AGPL&rdquo;, change &ldquo;2 or&rdquo; to &ldquo;3 or&rdquo;, and it "
